4Geeks Academy offers a course called "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer" that prepares students for a career in data science and machine learning. The course is designed for beginners and covers topics such as Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics. Students will learn to develop predictive models using libraries like Pandas and Numpy, and explore algorithms such as Close Neighbors and Decision Trees. The course includes real-life case studies and focuses on mastering industry-standard tools. The duration of the course is 16 weeks, with 3 classes held each week. Class sizes are kept small, with a maximum of 12 students. Upon completion, students receive a certificate recognized by multiple organizations. No previous experience is required, and students can choose between English and Spanish for the syllabus and content. For more information, visit the website: [https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop